    <item>
      <title>苹果公司 1100 亿美元的股票回购计划是美国历史上规模最大的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apple-s-110-billion-stock-buyback-plan-is-largest-in-us-history</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为全球最大的公司之一，苹果公司刚刚宣布了有史以来最大规模的美国回购计划，称其董事会批准了额外 1100 亿美元的股票回购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apple-s-110-billion-stock-buyback-plan-is-largest-in-us-history</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果的盈利和高通的乐观预测|彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-02/apple-s-earnings-and-qualcomm-s-upbeat-forecast-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者焦急地等待 iPhone 销售数据，彭博社的卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 和埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 在盘后分析了苹果公司的盈利预期。此外，与芯片制造商高通首席执行官的对话提供了乐观的预测，并与 DoorDash 的首席财务官讨论了该公司的最新业绩。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-02/apple-s-earnings-and-qualcomm-s-upbeat-forecast-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国主要立法者希望 FTC 调查 TikTok 利用儿童进行游说的情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-china-committee-wants-ftc-probe-into-tiktok-s-use-of-kids-to-lobby-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院主要议员呼吁联邦贸易委员会调查 TikTok 官员是否违反了保护儿童的法律，并利用这款流行应用敦促未成年用户游说国会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/us-china-committee-wants-ftc-probe-into-tiktok-s-use-of-kids-to-lobby-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:41:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果公司因乐观预测和创纪录的股票回购而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apple-sales-decline-less-than-feared-as-company-plots-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司上季度销售额强于预期，并预计本季度将恢复增长，引发了人们对经济放缓正在缓解的乐观情绪，该公司股价尾盘上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/apple-sales-decline-less-than-feared-as-company-plots-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
