      <title>Coinbase 第一季度利润和收入超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/coinbase-s-first-quarter-profit-revenue-top-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加密货币价格回升重新唤醒了个人投资者的需求，Coinbase Global Inc. 公布的第一季度收入和利润高于预期。]]></description>
